    I know Tuesday is busy at Papa Murphys, but this was a ridiculous visit! I called in an order at 2pm for pickup at 6pm. My order wasn't ready when I got there, I waited an additional 35 minutes before it was ready. People walked in and ordered after me and got their orders before me. There were at least 9 people working in the store. Stupid chaos, it's not as though you don't know Tuesday is going to be busy, why didn't someone make my order at 330 or whenever before it got busy.
